{
  "stem": "9728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Belgium, from Holland, from France, from Germany, from Austria, a lot of people came in to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lodz ghetto was more or less-- it was not a death camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not a dead, a death ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But people were dying there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People came from Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were quite-- fairly well fed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They came at Lodz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We did not have to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And people were dying like flies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My job at the cemetery was to carry the dead out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- in the ghetto was one horse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A horse and wagon collected every morning the dead-- some of them in the streets, some of them at homes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At this point, let me point out something else-- how the dead collection was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were given rations for so many people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some people, on account of the terrible hunger that we had, kept the dead people overnight, over two, three days, in order to collect the card so that they could get still the ration for the, for the dead people.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So some people were laying in their rooms dead two, three, up to four days, to wait until on Monday comes the new card route.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On Monday, I will get the card.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he will pick up the dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The collection of the dead-- the, the fellow drove around in a, in a horse and wagon and collected the dead and transported him to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The cemetery was a building, a huge building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a still cemetery from before the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the same building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for about the first year, I was working carrying out the dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Four people carried the dead, you know, on the stretchers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We carried them out to the grave.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
